ow: var(--shadow); } .page_header { display: flex; align-items: center; padding: 24px; background-color: var(--dark-bg); color: white; } .page_header img { height: 40px; margin-right: 16px; } .page_header .floating_element { font-size: 24px; font-weight: 600; } .content_section { padding: 24px; } .section_header_red { color: var(--accent-color); font-size: 32px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 24px; position: relative; padding-bottom: 10px; } .section_header_red::after { content: \&quot;\&quot;; position: absolute; bottom: 0; left: 0; width: 60px; height: 4px; background-color: var(--primary-color); border-radius: 2px; } .content_section_text p { margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 16px; } b { color: var(--primary-color); font-weight: 600; } tt { background-color: #e2e8f0; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 4px; font-family: 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 14px; } @media (max-width: 768px) { .main_page { margin: 20px auto; } .page_header { flex-direction: column; text-align: center; } .page_header img { margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 12px; } } </style> </head> <body> <div class=\&quot;main_page\&quot;> <div class=\&quot;page_header floating_element\&quot;> <img src=\&quot;./assets/favicon.svg\&quot; alt=\&quot;Ubuntu Logo\&quot; class=\&quot;floating_element\&quot;/> <span class=\&quot;floating_element\&quot;> Página por Defecto de Apache2 PackeTTrino </span> </div> <div class=\&quot;content_section floating_element\&quot;> <div class=\&quot;section_header section_header_red\&quot;> <div id=\&quot;about\&quot;></div> ¡Funciona! </div> <div class=\&quot;content_section_text\&quot;> <p> Esta es la página de bienvenida predeterminada que se utiliza para comprobar el correcto funcionamiento del servidor Apache2 PackeTTrino tras su instalación. Está basada en la página equivalente de Debian, de la cual se deriva el paquete de Apache en Ubuntu. Si puedes leer esta página, significa que el servidor HTTP Apache PackeTTrino instalado en este sitio está funcionando correctamente. Deberías <b>reemplazar este archivo</b> (ubicado en <tt>/var/www/html/index.html</tt>) antes de continuar usando tu servidor HTTP. </p> </div> </div> </div> </body> </html>&quot;}}}}}" resolved="true" dhclient="false" data-dhcp-server="" data-dhcp-lease-time="" data-dhcp-current-lease-time="" data-dhcp-flag-t1="false" data-dhcp-flag-t2="false" firewall-default-policy="{&quot;INPUT&quot;:&quot;ACCEPT&quot;,&quot;OUTPUT&quot;:&quot;ACCEPT&quot;,&quot;FORWARD&quot;:&quot;ACCEPT&quot;}" firewall-rules="{&quot;FILTER&quot;:[],&quot;NAT&quot;:[]}" browser="true" onclick="showPcMenu('pc-10')" oncontextmenu="showAdvancedOptions(event)" ondragstart="BoardItemDragStart(event)" ondrop="dropPackageOverItem(event); dropSwitchOverItem(event);" style="left: 1648px; top: 368px;" apache2="true"><img src="./assets/board/www-server.svg" alt="icon" draggable="false"><article class="modal-table arp-table" onclick="event.stopPropagation();"> <table> <tbody><tr> <th>IP</th> <th>MAC</th> </tr> </tbody></table> <button onclick="closeObjectModalTable(event, '.arp-table')">Cerrar</button> </article><article class="modal-table cache-dns-table" onclick="event.stopPropagation();"> <table> <tbody><tr> <th>Dominio</th> <th>Tipo de Registro</th> <th>Valor</th> </tr> </tbody></table> <button onclick="closeObjectModalTable(event, '.cache-dns-table')">Cerrar</button> </article><article class="modal-table routing-table" onclick="event.stopPropagation()"> <table> <tbody><tr> <th>Red de Destino</th> <th>Máscara de Red</th> <th>Salida</th> <th>Interfaz</th> <th>Siguiente Salto</th> </tr> </tbody><tbody><tr class="direct-route"> <td>80.60.60.0</td> <td>255.255.255.0</td> <td>80.60.60.15</td> <td>enp0s3</td> <td>0.0.0.0</td> </tr><tr class="default-route"> <td>0.0.0.0</td> <td>0.0.0.0</td> <td>80.60.60.15</td> <td>enp0s3</td> <td>80.60.60.1</td> </tr></tbody></table> <button onclick="closeObjectModalTable(event, '.routing-table')">Cerrar</button> </article><div class="advanced-options-modal modal" onc